sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor User as Grafana user
  participant UI as ChatInterface
  participant Context as contextService
  participant MCP as MCPClientProvider / mcpClient
  participant Filter as filterTools + truncateMessages
  participant LLM as llmService
  participant GrafanaLLM as Grafana LLM plugin
  participant Model as LLM provider
  participant Tools as Grafana MCP tools
  participant History as chatHistoryService

  User->>UI: Type question, attach files, or choose prompt
  UI->>Context: Read user, dashboard, variables, datasources
  Context-->>UI: Runtime context for system prompt

  UI->>MCP: listTools()
  MCP->>Tools: Fetch available Grafana MCP tools
  Tools-->>MCP: Tool definitions
  MCP-->>UI: Tool definitions
  UI->>Filter: convertToolsToOpenAI() + filterTools()
  Filter-->>UI: Allowed OpenAI-style tool list

  UI->>Filter: truncateMessages(messages, 10)
  Filter-->>UI: Bounded conversation history
  UI->>LLM: chat(messages, context, modelType, mcpClient, tools)

  LLM->>GrafanaLLM: llm.chatCompletions(messages, tools)
  GrafanaLLM->>Model: Request completion
  Model-->>GrafanaLLM: Text response or tool_calls
  GrafanaLLM-->>LLM: Assistant message

  alt Assistant returned tool_calls
    loop Up to 10 tool-call iterations
      LLM-->>UI: Mark tool call pending
      LLM->>MCP: callTool(name, arguments)
      MCP->>Tools: Execute Grafana MCP tool
      Tools-->>MCP: Tool result content
      MCP-->>LLM: Tool result
      LLM->>LLM: truncateToolResult(result.content)
      LLM->>GrafanaLLM: Follow-up chatCompletions(messages + tool result)
      GrafanaLLM->>Model: Continue completion
      Model-->>GrafanaLLM: Final text or more tool_calls
      GrafanaLLM-->>LLM: Assistant message
      LLM-->>UI: Update content and tool status
    end
  else No tool calls
    LLM-->>UI: Update assistant content
  end

  UI->>History: saveSession(finalMessages, currentSessionId)
  History-->>UI: Saved session id
  UI-->>User: Render markdown, code, mermaid, attachments, tool statuses
